# Copy this file to `.dev.vars` for local development with `wrangler dev`.
# For production, set these via `wrangler secret put <NAME>`.
#
# Required:
#   CF_GATEWAY_TOKEN     Cloudflare AI Gateway authenticated token (with Replicate provider key stored in Gateway).
#   API_KEYS             Comma-separated list of Bearer tokens accepted by this Worker.
#                        Generate strong random values (e.g. `openssl rand -base64 32`).
# Optional:
#   GITHUB_TOKEN         GitHub PAT used by scripts/ingest-docs.js to fetch Cloudflare docs.
#   REPLICATE_API_TOKEN  Only needed if you bypass AI Gateway and call Replicate directly.

CF_GATEWAY_TOKEN=
API_KEYS=
GITHUB_TOKEN=
REPLICATE_API_TOKEN=
